<doc id="965442" wikidata="Q949964" url="?curid=965442" title="Live in Chicago 12.19.98 at the United Center">
<text>Live in Chicago 12.19.98 at the United Center, also known as simply Live in Chicago 12.19.98, is a live album by the Dave Matthews Band, released by RCA on October 23, 2001. It was recorded at the United Center in Chicago, Illinois. It was originally broadcast as a live webcast, with the recording released on CD.

